{"tid":580022,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(減肥巴絲) 如下輕鬆減肥？","createTime":"2018-03-04T06:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T15:27:57.000Z","uid":45332,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"129ea2dfbdac4fabaa25ce20ba77a2f125e949ee","tid":580022,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:32:07.000Z","msg":"聽我啲朋友話<br />\n其實減肥係唔洗做好多運動，<br />\n只要控制飲食同做小量運動，就可以減到磅，<br />\n按你體重(磅數)乘15-18(睇你運動量定，冇運動直接十五)，再減返500就係你嘅每日卡路里攝取量<br />\n一磅脂肪3500卡路里，先試一個星期係唔係真係減到一磅。<br />\n要食早餐同中午，夜晚食野好多時大比例直接變脂肪。<br />\n仲有運動，例如跑步，唔洗長時間盡全力跑，<br />\n只要跑一分鐘令到你個心跳數上左去，<br />\n再偷懶快步行一兩分鐘再跑過就已經OK<br />\n<br />\n有冇過來人幫手睇下上面我聽返黎嘅啱唔啱？？<br />\n<br />\n利申：220磅大肥閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a8dae7d9ed8bc9d4b8d3e71580455aca632740","tid":580022,"uid":19657,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:39:58.000Z","msg":"去到200磅，8成都係飲食出問題，減甜減零食減油炸，已經輕咗第一步，另外重嘅人行步路都會吃力啲，所以畀正常人瘦得快，咁重唔建議做太多運動住，特別係跑步，每晚落樓急步行一個鐘，叫做踏出第一步先。<br />\n<br />\n最後最重要一點係恆心，得個講字做唔到以上全部係空談。"},{"pid":"fdd372542f0c1533591cf7c2a3b69d4b4fc8d6c0","tid":580022,"uid":162644,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:40:49.000Z","msg":"計呢d多舊魚<br />\n簡單諗只要你每日食既少於你每日所需既卡路里就得<br />\n樓主你220磅，你要keep住呢個體重必然你每日都食好多野，我就唔信你一日食三餐可以食到220磅<br />\n如果你一餐三四碗飯就另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再將你每餐份量減半一半或3分1<br />\n然後戒所有零食汽水有糖都免<br />\n持續一個月無輕過既話番黎搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820e04d3076f07467a615c94f6f916ece8e41ef3","tid":580022,"uid":54617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:41:20.000Z","msg":"肥婆晚晚要食牛腩<br />\n運動又唔做"},{"pid":"0e460dd569c8072350855b0ebd435b6e12b93bee","tid":580022,"uid":156331,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:41:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed2cc1d4243002eb65b6b2bf42c6aa339851523e","tid":580022,"uid":61678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:45:08.000Z","msg":"咁撚易瘦你而家都唔會係肥閪啦"},{"pid":"bc1056c5acb4ce628fb8f7b3b4457105a6a9075b","tid":580022,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"咁我嘅合理體重應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f75e9871778e9f60612cde0d0d6ad7040d95db","tid":580022,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"睇你肥底定廋底<br />\n肥底一定係要做多啲運動同BUILD MUSCLE<br />\n利申 肥底"},{"pid":"93c1e10bffa21c16f7b72dd2bc953422e4bfeb2c","tid":580022,"uid":143384,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"我由今年1月開始減，<br />\n頭一個月每星期做5日Gym，<br />\n負重為主，跑步輔助，<br />\n雖然一開始體重無點變，<br />\n但增左肌肉就會慢慢燃燒到脂肪，<br />\n我17x cm 90kg絲，到依加已經減左10kg，<br />\n新年仲要食左好多，又無做運動，但磅數仍然跌緊，<br />\n<br />\n我呢排都係用intermittent fasting唔食早餐，<br />\n下午1點至晚上8點都可以食嘢，其他時間只係飲水，<br />\n咁緊係唔係食垃圾食物啦，戒甜戒凍，<br />\n食high protein 嘅食物，碳水化合物就盡量減少，<br />\n最緊要係飲水！飲水！同飲水！<br />\n<br />\n大家同路人，要一齊加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf12b4e9b6617c3d17e112fd5f89eb12f48170c","tid":580022,"uid":133925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:54:01.000Z","msg":"之前胃痛，一痛就冇胃口食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾日就瘦左幾kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過呢d係唔健康嘅瘦。<br />\n絕食減肥係完全唔work，仲要對身體唔好，好易肥返。其實只要食少d零食，食多d水果蔬菜，間唔中做下運動就得。其實汁下屋，做下家務，行多幾層樓梯就得。"},{"pid":"8e55cbaefb88c301e107d969e73115bfe191fe3b","tid":580022,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:11:57.000Z","msg":"好<br />\n咁我依家每日兩餐<br />\n早餐雞肉三文治+500ml低糖豆漿(711)<br />\n午餐手撕雞(冇飯)<br />\n晚餐雞肉三文治<br />\n一日8L水<br />\nKeep三個星期<br />\n睇下減唔減到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n減到就開始做多啲帶氧運動，btw,溜冰算唔算？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f15abe09dce1acbddb480b41e7e323e855e0332","tid":580022,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"聽你朋友話乜鳩<br />\n你係瘦就唔會係大肥閪啦"},{"pid":"84b81f553e31131be3bb044f4c12cef9d477d58c","tid":580022,"uid":45332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f15abe09dce1acbddb480b41e7e323e855e0332","tid":580022,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"聽你朋友話乜鳩<br />\n你係瘦就唔會係大肥閪啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:16:10.000Z","msg":"吾你老母<br />\n系你老母<br />\n甘你老母<br />\n牙你老母"},{"pid":"aae8d57c5226c0523b52537d2c1a7e10755057f7","tid":580022,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93c1e10bffa21c16f7b72dd2bc953422e4bfeb2c","tid":580022,"uid":143384,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"我由今年1月開始減，<br />\n頭一個月每星期做5日Gym，<br />\n負重為主，跑步輔助，<br />\n雖然一開始體重無點變，<br />\n但增左肌肉就會慢慢燃燒到脂肪，<br />\n我17x cm 90kg絲，到依加已經減左10kg，<br />\n新年仲要食左好多，又無做運動，但磅數仍然跌緊，<br />\n<br />\n我呢排都係用intermittent fasting唔食早餐，<br />\n下午1點至晚上8點都可以食嘢，其他時間只係飲水，<br />\n咁緊係唔係食垃圾食物啦，戒甜戒凍，<br />\n食high protein 嘅食物，碳水化合物就盡量減少，<br />\n最緊要係飲水！飲水！同飲水！<br />\n<br />\n大家同路人，要一齊加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:17:38.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4994c74c1f5c928fa2ce5c81cb4f22aafaef53ea","tid":580022,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"84b81f553e31131be3bb044f4c12cef9d477d58c","tid":580022,"uid":45332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f15abe09dce1acbddb480b41e7e323e855e0332","tid":580022,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"聽你朋友話乜鳩<br />\n你係瘦就唔會係大肥閪啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:16:10.000Z","msg":"吾你老母<br />\n系你老母<br />\n甘你老母<br />\n牙你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:23:54.000Z","msg":"第一日上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"0a593e9e6cdd1e01728f9c6d0d6d557fd4df9ba5","tid":580022,"uid":35536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e55cbaefb88c301e107d969e73115bfe191fe3b","tid":580022,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:11:57.000Z","msg":"好<br />\n咁我依家每日兩餐<br />\n早餐雞肉三文治+500ml低糖豆漿(711)<br />\n午餐手撕雞(冇飯)<br />\n晚餐雞肉三文治<br />\n一日8L水<br />\nKeep三個星期<br />\n睇下減唔減到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n減到就開始做多啲帶氧運動，btw,溜冰算唔算？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:26:32.000Z","msg":"夠飽咩？你唔夠飽嘅話 即日都打回原形<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔食菜？水果？極度唔均衡飲食對身體冇益<br />\n<br />\n唔係唔食飯，但份量酌量減少，食多啲菜"},{"pid":"104ffff1cb20e30ca34fcbac3af0c80b5f7a7193","tid":580022,"uid":91093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:29:22.000Z","msg":"死左去啦肥到咁<br />\n到底要幾冇自制能力先可以咁撚肥？"},{"pid":"13f228cebb590b567c9f574868d724f24ec494c0","tid":580022,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a593e9e6cdd1e01728f9c6d0d6d557fd4df9ba5","tid":580022,"uid":35536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e55cbaefb88c301e107d969e73115bfe191fe3b","tid":580022,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:11:57.000Z","msg":"好<br />\n咁我依家每日兩餐<br />\n早餐雞肉三文治+500ml低糖豆漿(711)<br />\n午餐手撕雞(冇飯)<br />\n晚餐雞肉三文治<br />\n一日8L水<br />\nKeep三個星期<br />\n睇下減唔減到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n減到就開始做多啲帶氧運動，btw,溜冰算唔算？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:26:32.000Z","msg":"夠飽咩？你唔夠飽嘅話 即日都打回原形<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔食菜？水果？極度唔均衡飲食對身體冇益<br />\n<br />\n唔係唔食飯，但份量酌量減少，食多啲菜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:31:04.000Z","msg":"唔好飲豆漿"},{"pid":"9ee7c3dcc996fce6863d0b78318d1b5104a0f4db","tid":580022,"uid":35536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"做重量訓練係好有幫助<br />\n我keep住做咗3-4個月<br />\n加少少調節飲食 戒甜嘢 少啲啲飯<br />\n都減咗15磅<br />\n最緊要係身形都見到有變<br />\n褲頭都鬆哂"},{"pid":"e11ea88c8a9415851965db1b250699afa9fc9c3e","tid":580022,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T12:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e723a323938fb129857bf8144082a8a0ce14a2","tid":580022,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:31:07.000Z","msg":"前排日日落去跑街 係everyday咁跑1個鐘 <br />\n食個方面都少咗 <br />\n早餐一條蕉+一盒低糖豆漿 <br />\n午餐帶飯 7成菜 3成肉 波菜生菜西蘭花都試過 陪烚煙肉or烚三文魚粒<br />\n晚餐同早餐一樣 不過再飲杯綠茶先落街跑 綠茶有種唔知咩酸會可以消脂 紅茶都ok 不過冇綠茶咁多<br />\n記住飯同肉唔可以同一餐一齊食 好易將碳水化合物轉化成脂肪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一星期減咗4kg 不過本身都係好易肥好易瘦<br />\n可以食一餐火鍋肥3kg 落街瘋狂跑2個鐘又減1kg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4b3ee12cbc8d497b341844edc8ecb362d757e7","tid":580022,"uid":117638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:35:57.000Z","msg":"我個半月前開始減。6個星期瘦咗5kg，都冇乜點做運動，淨係飲大量水，早餐晚餐唔食carbohydrates，淨係食菜食肉。戒曬零食汽水，口痕就飲牛奶，食大豆棒。<br />\n<br />\n利申200磅大肥仔"},{"pid":"cf899b226c6b56ff7a657d5d9c229a8dcd329b6e","tid":580022,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"睇錯肥絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29dcd872c5227f558afa0dd50958c926404e6ab4","tid":580022,"uid":1444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:46:28.000Z","msg":"減少吸收澱粉質+適量嘅帶氧運動"},{"pid":"656fa3db72233f41cce448c5655b4b534ede93c6","tid":580022,"uid":27910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93c1e10bffa21c16f7b72dd2bc953422e4bfeb2c","tid":580022,"uid":143384,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"我由今年1月開始減，<br />\n頭一個月每星期做5日Gym，<br />\n負重為主，跑步輔助，<br />\n雖然一開始體重無點變，<br />\n但增左肌肉就會慢慢燃燒到脂肪，<br />\n我17x cm 90kg絲，到依加已經減左10kg，<br />\n新年仲要食左好多，又無做運動，但磅數仍然跌緊，<br />\n<br />\n我呢排都係用intermittent fasting唔食早餐，<br />\n下午1點至晚上8點都可以食嘢，其他時間只係飲水，<br />\n咁緊係唔係食垃圾食物啦，戒甜戒凍，<br />\n食high protein 嘅食物，碳水化合物就盡量減少，<br />\n最緊要係飲水！飲水！同飲水！<br />\n<br />\n大家同路人，要一齊加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:19:23.000Z","msg":"intermittent fasting其實掉返轉食早餐唔食夜晚得唔得架，姐係9至5先可以食野。"}]}